text: The Tikych () is a short river in Cherkasy Oblast, Ukraine. At its confluence with the Velyka Vys at Skaleva (Novoarkhanhelsk Raion), the Syniukha is formed.Синюха (река), Great Soviet Encyclopedia It is formed at the confluence of its source rivers Hnyly Tikych and Hirsky Tikych. ==References== Category:Rivers of Cherkasy Oblast
title: Tikych
